      "content": "StorSimple monitoring indicators | Microsoft Azure",
      "pos": [
        28,
        78
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Describes the light-emitting diodes (LEDs) and audible alarms used to monitor the status of the StorSimple device.",
      "pos": [
        98,
        212
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use StorSimple monitoring indicators to manage your device",
      "pos": [
        507,
        565
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Overview",
      "pos": [
        573,
        581
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Your StorSimple device includes light-emitting diodes (LEDs) and alarms that you can use to monitor the modules and overall status of the StorSimple device.",
      "pos": [
        583,
        739
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The monitoring indicators can be found on the hardware components of the device's primary enclosure and the EBOD enclosure.",
      "pos": [
        740,
        863
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The monitoring indicators can be either LEDs or audible alarms.",
      "pos": [
        864,
        927
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "There are three LED states used to indicate the status of a module: green, flashing green to red-amber, or red-amber.",
      "pos": [
        929,
        1046
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Green LEDs represent a healthy operating status.",
      "pos": [
        1052,
        1100
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Flashing green to red-amber LEDs represent the presence of non-critical conditions that might require user intervention.",
      "pos": [
        1105,
        1225
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Red-amber LEDs indicate that there is a critical fault present within the module.",
      "pos": [
        1230,
        1311
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The remainder of this article describes the various monitoring indicator LEDs, their locations on the StorSimple device, the device status based on the LED states, and any associated audible alarms.",
      "pos": [
        1315,
        1513
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Front panel indicator LEDs",
      "pos": [
        1518,
        1544
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The front panel, also known as the <bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>operations panel<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept> or <bpt id=\"p2\">*</bpt>ops panel<ept id=\"p2\">*</ept>, displays the aggregate status of all the modules in the system.",
      "pos": [
        1546,
        1679
      ]
    },
    {
